{"tid":771374,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"撩鼻屎係好滿足嘅一件事","createTime":"2018-08-08T01:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T04:07:53.000Z","uid":65443,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2889a0d3790bd862209b9026dd2e303b4c35ad3b","tid":771374,"uid":65443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"但係硬晒一粒粒同埋仲係水汪汪果啲唔過癮。最正係啲鼻屎未乾晒，黐lup lup，一撩就黐住成抽啡色咁出黎。通常愈大pat同愈黐lup lup 就愈有快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黐完出黎之後，個鼻暢通返，隱隱仲聞到抽鼻屎嘅臭味，成個人都特別醒神，做野都有心機啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家已經養成朝朝返公司就撩鼻屎嘅習慣。有時要開會冇得撩，就全日都周身唔聚財，頭赤赤咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 晏啲先撩返，佢就可能已經變咗粒狀鼻屎，冇晒黏性，唔再滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最衰就係撩鼻屎好似打J咁，撩完之後要等一輪先有。如果要高質鼻屎就要忍手唔好撩，等第二日佢成形同儲返咁上下量先去撩。雖然等待嘅時間好痛苦，但當撩到pat perfect鼻屎出黎嘅時候，個感覺就好似成個禮拜唔打J，儲埋一次過內射女神咁，個滿足感係非筆墨所能形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fcc3d286b580c5c3dbd80fdb6ef465020ec904","tid":771374,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"走開啦 核突佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40017cbb831cca3995ee12a01fbee213722f696b","tid":771374,"uid":20914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"食埋重好，醒腦醒神"},{"pid":"8a4ada007eead35bbbacfb3037c1c6cb770644b1","tid":771374,"uid":65443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}